# 🤖 Family Telegram Bot — MVP Specification

---

## 🎯 Goal

Provide a frictionless way to coordinate a weekly family call across time zones:

* No manual time calculations
* No free-text input (except fallback)
* Minimal interaction (buttons only)
* Event-based confirmation (not voting)

---

## 🧩 Core Principles

* Use Telegram Bot API inline buttons for all interactions
* Store **one canonical time** (base timezone)
* Display **all times in user’s local timezone**
* Model = **event invite with negotiation**, not poll

---

## 🗂️ Data Model

```yaml
settings:
  default_time: "10:00"
  base_timezone: "America/Vancouver"
  poll_enabled: true
  poll_schedule: "Friday 12:00"
  auto_confirm_hours: 12

users:
  user_id:
    name: string
    timezone: string

event:
  current_time: datetime
  status: idle | proposed | confirmed
  proposal_author: user_id
  responses:
    user_id: yes | no | pending
  deadline: datetime
```

