## 🔄 Time Proposal Flow

---

### Time Options Generation

* Range: `-2h → +3h` from `default_time`

```python
options = [
  base_time - 2h,
  base_time - 1h,
  base_time,
  base_time + 1h,
  base_time + 2h,
  base_time + 3h
]
```

* Convert each → user local time before display

