## 🔁 Confirmation Logic (Event-Based)

### State Machine

```text
idle → proposed → confirmed
        ↑
        └── new proposal
```

---

### Rules

* New proposal:

  * resets all responses
* Any ❌:

  * proposal rejected
* Any 🔄:

  * replaces proposal
* All ✅:

  * confirmed
* No objections within timeout:

  * auto-confirm

---

## ⏱️ Auto-Confirm

Trigger:

* No ❌ responses
* `deadline` reached

**Message (RU):**

```text
✅ Время подтверждено автоматически:

➡️ 11:00
```

