## ⏳ Delay Handling

On selection:

**Message (RU):**

```text
⏳ Сдвигаем на 5 минут

Новое время: 10:05
```

---

### Constraints

* First click wins
* Lock further changes for 2–3 minutes

---

## 🕒 Scheduler (Cron)

| Event         | Action                   |
| ------------- | ------------------------ |
| Friday        | Send invite              |
| On proposal   | Start auto-confirm timer |
| Sunday -5 min | Send reminder            |
| Sunday        | Start call               |

